Thai authorities at Phuket island's famous Patang beach, for  example, are now hoping to seize the opportunity to remove sloppy  oceanfront shops and stalls and rebuild in a way that would better  preserve the beach's natural beauty.
JAKARTA, Jan. 16 (Xinhua)-- The Indonesian government Sunday  sent a research vessel to the west coast of tsunami-devastated  Aceh to conduct survey of the ocean floor around the zone of the  earthquake on Dec. 26 last year.
